Game
====

Config
------
You can configure server using conf file. See config for further details.
Client may be configured only by command line.

Client
------
First you connect to the server using comand line parameters.
Once all the clients connect (players number >= 0.7 * number speciefied by server conf)
every player set his ready and the game starts.

Gameplay
--------
Each tank can shoot or use ability every turn.
Only one tank shoots at the time.

Victory
-------
The winner is the tank that stays last alive.
In other words, all other tanks are destroyed.
